Which resources can be assigned the Contributor role for VM1?

discussion.content:
Selected Answer: A
Answer is A;

You can assign a role to a user, group, service principal, or managed identity. This is also called a security principal.
https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/role-based-access-control/role-assignments-steps#step-1-determine-who-needs-access


Cannot be a dynamic group;
